{"id":635798,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/cds档案-｜-疫情期间的官方穿帮宣传/","date":"2020-02-18T19:31:42Z","modified":"2020-02-19T01:59:51Z","title":"CDS档案 ｜ 疫情期间的官方穿帮宣传","content":"<p>CDT编者按：随着全民动员起来防控疫情之后，官媒也开始了声势浩大的造势运动，除了去武汉病房挖“感动中国”的故事之外，也一如既往地制造出“感动中国”的故事，当然，也总是被眼尖的网友识破。CDT编辑收集一些“穿帮”宣传。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong> 1 这也会撞衫吗？</strong></p>\n<p>CCTV中文国际2月7日播出的宣传短片《 记者探访武昌方舱医院》，其中一位病人与另一个宣传片中出现的人穿着一模一样的衣服。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635915\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-7.png 608w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-7-300x298.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-7-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-7-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635914\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/2-14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/2-14.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/2-14-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/2-14-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/2-14-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/2-14-1080x608.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635916\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13.jpg 1078w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13-768x768.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13-440x440.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-13-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>2 群众女演员非常忙</strong></p>\n<p>2月7日，澎湃新闻视频报道<a href=\"https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_5820765\">《战疫者丨女护士隔玻璃凝望男友：抱抱我》</a>拍摄了浙大四院感染楼门口，95后护士陈颖与男友隔门对望的场景。很快网友发现，这位女护士与新闻联播中武汉汉江方舱医院首批出院患者张芬非常相似。此外，澎湃的新闻视频播出后，随即穿帮，<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%98%af%e6%8a%97%e7%96%ab%e5%a5%b3%e6%8a%a4%e5%a3%ab%ef%bc%9f%e8%bf%98%e6%98%af%e5%85%bc%e8%81%8c%e6%bc%94%e5%91%98%ef%bc%9f/\">【立此存照】看官媒如何造新闻：是抗疫女护士？还是兼职演员？  </a></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635917\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/5-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/5-6.jpg 361w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/5-6-113x300.jpg 113w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>甚至有网友找出之前央视的“群众演员”与女护士、女患者进行对比：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635918\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"373\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-1-1.jpg 558w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/3-1-1-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635919\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-9.jpg 558w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/4-9-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>3 千里复制</strong></p>\n<p>2月15日，武汉和寿光都下雪了，两个一模一样的小区都有业主在雪地里绘制一只紧握的拳头，中国加油。</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-635921 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/6-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/6-3.jpg 1168w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/6-3-300x277.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/6-3-1024x947.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/6-3-768x710.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/6-3-1080x999.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>4 出生不到20天的双胞胎开口说话</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635922\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/7-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/7-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/7-3-150x300.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/7-3-512x1024.jpg 512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/7-3-768x1536.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/7-3-1024x2048.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>5 哑巴也能说话</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635923\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"990\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-18.jpg 404w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-18-152x300.jpg 152w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with CDS档案\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\" rel=\"tag\">CDS档案</a>|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":296,"categories":[18271,38827,38895,38912,38960,39707],"tags":[38867,39820,39648,39819]}